      	<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">

      		<p n="1-3">
      			Twelfth year of the victorious king Narasiṃhavarman.
      		</p>
      		<p n="3-5">
      			Paṇaya Nāttaṉ, the servant <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Pakaimatar of Pācāṟu in Mīkoṉṟaināṭu, fell recapturing cattle.
      		</p>

      	</div>

